On the outward flight, employees refused Jaupgrade Jaqueline, even though she had shown a mail in which Cathay Pacific allegedly promised an upgrade. The luencer claims to have received the letter from an airline marketing employee. However, the airline accuses Jaqueline of falsifying the mail.
